Can a Christian be a full fledged Trump supporter?

37:21.090 --> 37:22.933
All Trump supporters are Christians.

37:22.953 --> 37:24.935
That's the whole thing.

37:24.955 --> 37:25.897
I thought that was the whole deal.

37:26.017 --> 37:27.759
That's, yeah.

37:27.779 --> 37:29.121
I thought that was what it was.

37:29.141 --> 37:30.323
He's God's chosen man.

37:30.823 --> 37:31.765
What are you talking about?

37:31.785 --> 37:33.727
Sorry.

37:34.949 --> 37:35.049
Yeah.

37:35.069 --> 37:38.814
No, I don't think a Christian should identify as a full fledged Trump supporter.

37:39.455 --> 37:41.478
Like I'm talking about like a rabid fan.

37:41.678 --> 37:45.904
Like, you know, you know, like, I don't think I don't think Christians to treat any man.

37:46.625 --> 37:47.647
Yeah, especially.

37:47.767 --> 37:48.308
Absolutely.

37:49.049 --> 37:49.149
Yeah.

37:49.169 --> 37:50.130
No matter who he is.

37:50.306 --> 37:50.626
Right.

37:51.087 --> 38:04.164
And it is like it is disconcerting just to see the level of rabbit-ness and borderline worship of Trump by some very conservative people.

38:04.444 --> 38:07.408
And it's a little weird to see.

38:07.428 --> 38:08.329
A little weird.

