01:02:38.722 --> 01:02:42.107
Um, and it might get tougher once you become a parent.

01:02:43.549 --> 01:03:01.693
Um, but I would say if you want to, if you want to work on one thing that would pair you most for being a parent, it would be that disciplined flexibility over, over routine.

01:03:02.955 --> 01:03:05.298
Like I think, um,

01:03:05.826 --> 01:03:08.791
How do you handle situations when they change last minute?

01:03:10.854 --> 01:03:16.404
