01:03:38.849 --> 01:03:43.178
Did they train you how to handle an unexpected situation?

01:03:43.839 --> 01:03:44.861
Yes.

01:03:46.263 --> 01:03:56.082
That's actually a good point because the battlefield is a very good analogy for being a parent because they train you that

01:03:56.354 --> 01:03:58.276
You know, we're going to train you how to do things this way.

01:03:58.296 --> 01:04:00.939
